snippet.title: Death Front - Official Teaser Trailer | IndieMania Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Death Front is a first-person shooter with supernatural elements. Team up in parties of four to uncover the mystery behind a series of gruesome murders while being haunted by ghosts. Do you have what it takes to face these sinister forces? Check out the creepy teaser trailer for Death Front ahead of the game's release in 2024 on PC.
